Find $\sec 135^\circ.$
inference:
$\sec 135^\circ = \frac{1}{\cos 135^\circ}$

$\cos 135^\circ = \cos (180^\circ - 45^\circ) = -\cos 45^\circ = -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}$

$\sec 135^\circ = \frac{1}{-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}} = -\sqrt{2}$

Final Answer: $\boxed{-\sqrt{2}}$. I hope it is correct.
